Modulation of toxicity effects of CuSO(4) by sulfated polysaccharides extracted 
from brown algae (Sargassum tenerrimum) in Danio rerio as a model.

Zargari A(1), Nejatian M(2)(3), Abbaszadeh S(4)(5), Jahanbin K(6), Bagheri T(7), 
